The '''Yuzzem''' were large, heavy, furred [[Humanoid/Legends|humanoids]] with long snouts and large black [[Eye/Legends|eyes]]. Their [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] was the forested [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Ragna III]]. They were quite strong and temperamental. They fought fiercely, and their large size made them hard to subdue. Yuzzem also adhered to strict codes of honor and debt-fulfillment.<ref name="EGAS" />

Because of their strength and intelligence, many [[Scientist/Legends|scientists]] believed the Yuzzem to be distant relatives of the [[Wookiee/Legends|Wookiees]].<ref name="EGAS" />

==History==
[[File:Yuzzem_EGTA.png|thumb|left|180px|A Yuzzem.]]
During the [[Separatist Crisis/Legends|Separatist Crisis]] preceding the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]], at least two Yuzzem guards were in employ of Bossban [[Soergg Vosadii Bezhin]] who had strong ties with the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Separatists]].<ref name="TAS">''[[The Approaching Storm]]''</ref> Afterward, the [[Confederacy of Independent Systems/Legends|Confederacy of Independent Systems]] used them to [[Battle of Aargonar (Clone Wars)|fight]] on [[Aargonar/Legends|Aargonar]].<ref name="Enemy Lines">[[Republic 59|''Republic'' 59]]</ref> The [[Galactic Empire/Legends|Galactic Empire]] enslaved the species as they had done to the Wookiees and were employed for heavy labor such as mining. However, because of their strength and their ill-temperament, the Imperials had trouble making them work as slaves.<ref name="EGAS" /> The species also had long [[Wikipedia:hangover|hangovers]] due to their massive size.<ref name="SotME">''[[Splinter of the Mind's Eye]]''</ref>

During their adventures on [[Mimban/Legends|Mimban]] searching for the [[Kaiburr crystal]], [[Luke Skywalker/Legends|Luke Skywalker]] and [[Princess/Legends|Princess]] [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa]] were helped by two Yuzzem, [[Hin]] and [[Kee (Yuzzem)|Kee]]. Both were slain by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Darth Vader]].<ref name="SotME" />

In [[44 ABY]], a Yuzzem [[Jedi Master/Legends|Jedi Master]], [[Barratk'l]], joined the [[Jedi High Council (New Jedi Order)|Jedi High Council]].<ref name="Vortex">''[[Fate of the Jedi: Vortex]]''</ref>

